retoucheBD: software to improve digital comics for e-readers
 
retoucheBD may be used for improving the orientation of an inclined image.

The bash script comics2pdf.sh is used for making a .pdf file from a .cbz 
or a .cbr file.

Requirements:
	OpenCv
	unzip/unrar
	pdflatex
	
Compiling (needs opencv):
	make
  
Running:
	./retouche_BD
 

Use A4intoA5.sh to cut any A4 pdf into A5 for ereaders!

 
